WEBVTT

01:35.830 --> 01:41.280
[Pursuit of Jade]

01:41.380 --> 01:43.910
[Episode 34]

01:45.840 --> 01:49.900
Your Majesty, Prime Minister Wei
and Grand Tutor Li request an audience.

01:54.759 --> 01:55.759
Dear ministers,

01:56.000 --> 01:57.400
what brings you to see me?

01:58.640 --> 01:59.440
Your Majesty,

02:00.000 --> 02:02.350
I wish to impeach
Prime Minister Wei's son, Wei Xuan,

02:02.350 --> 02:03.930
for forcibly levying winter grain,
oppressing the people into revolt,

02:03.930 --> 02:05.510
and deserting the army.

02:05.510 --> 02:06.750
After returning to the capital
without permission,

02:06.750 --> 02:08.110
he treated human life as worthless.

02:08.110 --> 02:09.400
If he is not punished
for all these crimes,

02:09.400 --> 02:11.000
Heaven will not tolerate it!

02:13.270 --> 02:15.000
Grand Tutor, don't be so hasty.

02:15.870 --> 02:17.870
What do you mean
by treating human life as worthless?

02:17.870 --> 02:19.000
Prime Minister Wei!

02:19.590 --> 02:22.470
Your son broke my young grandson's leg.

02:22.470 --> 02:24.190
He might be crippled
for the rest of his life!

02:24.190 --> 02:26.360
Was that a counter-stratagem,

02:26.360 --> 02:29.020
or is he innocent
and actually deserves credit?

02:29.030 --> 02:29.829
Your Majesty!

02:29.960 --> 02:31.570
If there is someone in our court

02:31.570 --> 02:33.430
who wields unchecked power
and cannot be criticized,

02:33.430 --> 02:34.630
then I will have no choice

02:34.630 --> 02:36.430
but to beat the Petition Drum

02:36.430 --> 02:39.520
and let the world judge!

02:39.840 --> 02:40.360
Well...

02:40.590 --> 02:41.280
Fine.

02:42.120 --> 02:44.520
I am willing to join you.

02:45.150 --> 02:45.680
Don't...

02:46.079 --> 02:48.910
Your Majesty,
for the sake of your dignity,

02:48.910 --> 02:50.910
I have endured all kinds of humiliation.

02:50.910 --> 02:52.190
But Li Huaiqin

02:52.520 --> 02:54.540
claims that my wife and I are on bad terms

02:54.540 --> 02:56.070
and that my son is a bastard!

02:56.470 --> 02:57.430
He even says

02:57.630 --> 02:59.400
that I still love my childhood sweetheart,

02:59.400 --> 03:00.710
and that my true love is in the harem!

03:00.710 --> 03:01.840
Such remarks

03:01.840 --> 03:03.520
involve the late Emperor

03:03.520 --> 03:05.180
and many secrets of the harem.

03:05.810 --> 03:09.140
And now the Li family is making
presumptuous speculations.

03:09.520 --> 03:10.280
Fine.

03:10.800 --> 03:13.560
I will accompany you to the Petition Drum,

03:13.590 --> 03:15.120
and we'll make everything

03:15.120 --> 03:16.520
perfectly clear

03:16.520 --> 03:17.520
in front of the whole world!

03:17.520 --> 03:18.050
Let's go!

03:19.079 --> 03:20.540
You are talking nonsense!

03:20.630 --> 03:23.960
When did the Li family ever speculate
about you and the ha...

03:24.560 --> 03:25.360
Your Majesty!

03:25.560 --> 03:26.280
I didn't!

03:26.280 --> 03:27.520
-I didn't, Your Majesty!
-You just said that!

03:27.520 --> 03:28.310
And now you're denying it?

03:28.310 --> 03:29.840
Ministers, please don't get angry.

03:29.840 --> 03:31.190
Let's talk this over calmly.

03:31.190 --> 03:33.000
Grand Tutor Li
constantly spreads slander in court.

03:33.000 --> 03:34.710
I fear even Your Majesty
finds it hard to judge fairly.

03:34.710 --> 03:36.590
You must explain this clearly!

03:36.590 --> 03:37.120
Let's go!

03:37.520 --> 03:37.960
Your Majesty!

03:37.960 --> 03:38.470
Ministers!

03:38.470 --> 03:39.120
I am wrongly accused!

03:39.120 --> 03:40.000
Who accused you wrongly?

03:40.000 --> 03:41.840
It is clearly
Wei Yan who deceives everyone

03:41.840 --> 03:44.280
and has no respect for you, Your Majesty!

03:44.680 --> 03:46.150
-Your Majesty!
-Don't let it cause a rift between you!

03:46.150 --> 03:46.960
Your Majesty!

03:52.870 --> 03:54.840
Fine! Since you won't listen,

03:55.240 --> 03:56.970
I won't be the Emperor anymore!

03:58.750 --> 03:59.960
-I'll just abdicate! Alright?
-Stop it!

03:59.960 --> 04:00.770
You cannot!

04:03.240 --> 04:05.280
As the Emperor,

04:05.280 --> 04:06.800
how can you take off your dragon robe
so easily?

04:06.800 --> 04:07.800
Presumptuously!

04:08.840 --> 04:10.040
How dare you, Wei Yan!

04:10.470 --> 04:13.890
How dare you speak so arrogantly
to His Majesty!

04:14.120 --> 04:16.480
I think you're the one who is acting

04:16.630 --> 04:17.800
presumptuously!

04:21.360 --> 04:22.820
I was wrong, Your Majesty.

04:23.000 --> 04:24.060
Alright, alright.

04:24.830 --> 04:27.510
You two were just acting
in the heat of the moment.

04:27.510 --> 04:28.950
So was I.

04:29.510 --> 04:30.240
In short,

04:30.360 --> 04:32.000
it is all because Li Huaiqin
lacked virtue after drinking

04:32.000 --> 04:33.260
and spoke recklessly.

04:36.040 --> 04:37.510
But since his leg is already broken

04:37.510 --> 04:38.680
and he has been punished,

04:38.680 --> 04:41.010
I will send a royal physician
to treat him.

04:41.159 --> 04:42.240
After he recovers,

04:42.330 --> 04:44.310
he will be sent to the Imperial College
to study and repent

04:44.310 --> 04:45.909
to cultivate his character.

04:48.870 --> 04:51.740
As for Wei Xuan injuring someone...

04:52.190 --> 04:54.120
although there were
extenuating circumstances,

04:54.120 --> 04:56.020
the state has its laws.

04:56.190 --> 04:58.190
Use of private punishment is wrong.

04:58.240 --> 05:01.430
I... I will remove him from his post
as Military Commissioner for now.

05:01.430 --> 05:03.600
He can atone for his crimes
by earning merits in the future.

05:03.600 --> 05:04.310
Anyway,

05:05.600 --> 05:08.080
if I hear any more filthy rumors

05:08.100 --> 05:10.760
concerning the reputation
of the royal family,

05:11.070 --> 05:13.070
do not blame me for showing no mercy.

05:17.680 --> 05:19.940
-Yes, Your Majesty!
-Yes, Your Majesty!

05:33.830 --> 05:34.750
Your Majesty...

05:34.750 --> 05:35.880
Your Majesty. Gone.

05:37.600 --> 05:39.290
Your Majesty, please quell your anger!

05:39.290 --> 05:40.090
Your Majesty,

05:40.430 --> 05:41.510
in this case,

05:41.510 --> 05:44.430
Grand Tutor Li might become alienated
from us.

05:44.430 --> 05:45.540
Then what do you think I should have done?

05:45.540 --> 05:46.800
Tell me!

05:46.920 --> 05:47.920
What should we do?

05:49.310 --> 05:50.450
Now that Xie Zheng is back,

05:50.450 --> 05:52.240
Wei Yan has become emboldened!

05:52.510 --> 05:53.870
Wei Yan came here today

05:53.870 --> 05:55.040
clearly to slap me in the face

05:55.040 --> 05:57.440
and break our alliance
with Grand Tutor Li!

05:58.850 --> 06:00.510
These two old turtles.

06:00.800 --> 06:02.070
It's always one side overpowering

06:02.070 --> 06:03.680
the other between these two.

06:04.240 --> 06:05.720
When will a third party

06:05.720 --> 06:06.630
get involved?

06:13.510 --> 06:15.570
My Lord, what did His Majesty say?

06:15.720 --> 06:17.450
That useless trash, Qi Sheng.

06:17.950 --> 06:20.620
Such a fence-sitter. He changed his mind.

06:21.000 --> 06:21.480
Well...

06:25.240 --> 06:26.830
Now that Xie Zheng has returned,

06:26.830 --> 06:29.950
Wei Yan has become even more powerful.

06:31.040 --> 06:33.570
It seems we can no longer rely on
His Majesty.

06:34.270 --> 06:35.360
The Li family

06:36.360 --> 06:38.400
must find another way out.

06:41.830 --> 06:42.430
Master,

06:43.580 --> 06:45.890
Qi Min is likely to make a big move soon.

06:46.390 --> 06:47.070
Also,

06:47.480 --> 06:49.409
there's news regarding
the past events in Jinzhou that

06:49.409 --> 06:50.310
the Prime Minister ordered
to be investigated.

06:50.310 --> 06:51.390
[To Grand Tutor, My Lord: I have been
tirelessly investigating day and night,]

06:51.310 --> 06:53.220
The news came from Chongzhou.

06:51.390 --> 06:52.390
[and have finally uncovered a key clue
in the old case, going back 17 years,]

06:52.390 --> 06:52.890
[concerning
the troop deployment Tiger Tally]

06:52.890 --> 06:53.390
[once held by Wei Qilin,
a household general of the Wei family.]

06:54.040 --> 06:54.980
Do you think

06:55.159 --> 06:57.490
we should inform the Eldest Young Master?

07:00.870 --> 07:02.320
Seventeen years ago,

07:02.480 --> 07:06.080
the Tiger Tally that Wei Qilin used
to deploy the troops was real.

07:06.680 --> 07:09.710
But it became a fake
when it reached Lord Changxin.

07:10.720 --> 07:13.430
Between the real and fake Tiger Tallies,

07:13.430 --> 07:14.920
the most critical link

07:16.400 --> 07:18.850
was the person who delivered it.

07:24.680 --> 07:25.800
Wei Qilin.

07:27.820 --> 07:30.140
[Wei Residence]

07:34.360 --> 07:35.870
After all these days,

07:36.360 --> 07:38.690
you finally have the courage to come back.

07:48.720 --> 07:49.920
I heard Mother is ill.

07:50.800 --> 07:52.130
I was worried about her.

07:57.430 --> 07:58.890
As for Li Huaiqin's leg...

07:59.310 --> 08:00.870
I'll take responsibility
for my own actions.

08:00.870 --> 08:02.130
Take responsibility?

08:03.720 --> 08:05.870
Are you worthy of taking responsibility

08:05.870 --> 08:07.670
for the Wei family's lost honor?

08:08.750 --> 08:10.550
And are you really capable of it?

08:14.510 --> 08:15.560
I've taken care of

08:15.920 --> 08:17.380
the official procedures.

08:18.560 --> 08:20.160
But you can't avoid

08:20.920 --> 08:22.360
the family punishment.

08:23.680 --> 08:24.490
Guards.

08:25.070 --> 08:25.480
Here!

08:28.070 --> 08:28.800
Twelve!

08:29.270 --> 08:29.870
Thirteen!

08:30.640 --> 08:31.240
Fourteen!

08:31.830 --> 08:32.429
Fifteen!

08:33.270 --> 08:33.870
Sixteen!

08:34.960 --> 08:35.620
Seventeen!

08:36.200 --> 08:36.799
Eighteen!

08:37.860 --> 08:39.120
Punishment complete.

08:42.000 --> 08:42.679
Father.

08:45.000 --> 08:46.150
Mother is sick.

08:47.840 --> 08:49.700
Won't you go and keep her company?

08:50.440 --> 08:53.310
I have had someone
fetch a royal physician.

08:53.360 --> 08:54.150
Do you know why

08:54.150 --> 08:56.200
I broke Li Huaiqin's leg that day?

08:57.460 --> 08:58.660
He insulted me.

08:59.760 --> 09:01.990
He said I'm not your son!

09:03.120 --> 09:04.290
He said that your true love
is your childhood sweetheart

09:04.290 --> 09:05.550
who's in the harem now.

09:06.120 --> 09:07.030
My mother

09:07.910 --> 09:09.910
has been serving you all these years

09:10.000 --> 09:11.600
and gave everything for you.

09:12.200 --> 09:13.870
But now that she lies sick in bed,

09:13.870 --> 09:16.270
you can't even spare a glance
for your wife?

09:18.910 --> 09:19.840
Prime Minister.

09:21.030 --> 09:22.320
A letter from Wei Sheng.

09:22.320 --> 09:24.180
It concerns the Marquis of Wu'an.

09:30.320 --> 09:31.240
See?

09:32.600 --> 09:34.530
I have official affairs to handle.

09:35.960 --> 09:37.360
As for your mother,

09:38.030 --> 09:39.230
take good care of her.

09:40.150 --> 09:41.550
If there is nothing else,

09:41.910 --> 09:42.720
stay put

09:42.720 --> 09:44.120
and don't wander around.

09:44.230 --> 09:46.760
You have only ever had Xie Zheng
in your heart!

09:47.390 --> 09:50.120
Have you ever considered
Mother and me as family?

09:52.870 --> 09:54.030
I guessed right.

09:55.270 --> 09:57.440
You care for Xie Zheng

09:57.630 --> 09:59.320
like he's your own.

09:59.840 --> 10:01.270
You poured all your energy

10:01.270 --> 10:02.390
and all your care

10:02.390 --> 10:04.790
into him alone.

10:05.960 --> 10:06.960
And I...

10:07.200 --> 10:10.150
I can only watch helplessly
from the sidelines!

10:15.730 --> 10:18.110
Have you ever really looked at me?

10:19.150 --> 10:20.150
Even once,

10:20.600 --> 10:22.200
just once?

10:23.120 --> 10:24.000
What I hate most

10:24.000 --> 10:25.960
is this indifferent look of yours!

10:26.030 --> 10:26.840
Since I was little,

10:26.840 --> 10:28.720
no matter what I did,

10:28.720 --> 10:30.200
you never cared!

10:31.150 --> 10:32.470
Is Xie Zheng your son,

10:32.470 --> 10:34.080
or am I?

10:34.080 --> 10:35.960
Am I just a bastard you took in?

10:36.440 --> 10:37.240
Am I?

11:29.870 --> 11:32.240
You are not a child anymore.

11:57.640 --> 12:00.040
[Where Compassion and Grace Meet]

11:57.870 --> 12:00.320
The Princess Royal is here!

12:00.750 --> 12:02.030
Your Highness,

12:02.270 --> 12:03.910
His Majesty is busy with state affairs.

12:03.910 --> 12:05.440
Please calm your anger, Your Majesty!

12:05.440 --> 12:07.910
I couldn't stop Her Highness!

12:10.510 --> 12:11.270
Never mind.

12:11.320 --> 12:12.720
I didn't expect you to stop her.

12:12.720 --> 12:13.510
Leave us.

12:14.080 --> 12:15.140
Yes, Your Majesty.

12:16.840 --> 12:20.370
Brother, I heard you want to marry me off
to the Marquis of Wu'an?

12:23.670 --> 12:24.510
Sister,

12:24.960 --> 12:27.570
I've found you a peerless hero
for a husband.

12:27.790 --> 12:29.240
Why are you displeased?

12:32.030 --> 12:33.120
I'll beat you to death!

12:33.120 --> 12:34.000
Stop beating me, Sister!

12:34.000 --> 12:34.440
Don't run!

12:34.440 --> 12:35.080
It hurts!

12:35.730 --> 12:37.840
Didn't you say
you liked the Marquis of Wu'an before?

12:37.840 --> 12:39.640
And that you wanted to marry him?

12:40.030 --> 12:41.370
I was only 6 then!

12:41.600 --> 12:42.490
Six years old!

12:43.150 --> 12:44.440
-You just want to get the Marquis of Wu'an on our side!
-Sister!

12:44.440 --> 12:45.480
-Stop beating me!
-Taking my marriage as an excuse!

12:45.480 --> 12:46.870
It won't look good if you keep beating me!

12:46.870 --> 12:48.240
You care about that?

12:49.390 --> 12:51.200
First you sold me to the Li family,

12:51.200 --> 12:52.630
and now you're selling me
to the Xie family.

12:52.630 --> 12:54.290
Am I still the Princess Royal?

12:54.440 --> 12:55.960
Don't I deserve any dignity?

12:55.960 --> 12:57.560
Don't I deserve any dignity?

12:57.870 --> 12:59.030
You are a Qi too.

12:59.030 --> 12:59.790
Can you really bear to watch me

12:59.790 --> 13:02.120
be manipulated by those two old bastards?

13:09.080 --> 13:11.210
I've been living in fear all this time,

13:12.000 --> 13:15.300
and it has been 17 years, Sister.

13:15.920 --> 13:19.430
Sister, you are well-read.

13:19.460 --> 13:24.270
Have you ever seen
such a cowardly emperor as me?

13:26.360 --> 13:27.910
Xie Zheng is not Wei Yan.

13:28.670 --> 13:31.000
Even without a marriage alliance
as leverage,

13:31.000 --> 13:32.930
he can still be of use to you.

13:33.080 --> 13:34.870
Then, Sister,

13:35.600 --> 13:37.390
can you vouch for him forever?

13:38.480 --> 13:39.600
Lord Changxin...

13:39.600 --> 13:41.320
Seventeen years ago, Lord Changxin...

13:41.320 --> 13:43.790
never imagined he would rebel either.

13:45.000 --> 13:46.510
Didn't they say

13:46.510 --> 13:48.390
his entire family was dead?

13:48.390 --> 13:50.720
Then how... how did this story end up

13:50.740 --> 13:53.540
with Sui Yuanhuai
faking his death and escaping?

13:59.910 --> 14:00.700
Anyway,

14:01.080 --> 14:02.910
stop playing matchmaker.

14:03.000 --> 14:04.330
Or I'll come back again.

14:04.480 --> 14:06.200
This time in the army,

14:06.670 --> 14:08.130
I may not have learned much else,

14:08.130 --> 14:09.140
but I've learned

14:09.890 --> 14:11.440
how to fight.

14:11.860 --> 14:14.410
Alright, I get it. I'm scared.

14:27.750 --> 14:30.000
Go get Li Xiang immediately!

14:30.510 --> 14:31.390
Hurry!

14:31.510 --> 14:32.630
Losing an ear

14:32.630 --> 14:33.910
won't kill him!

14:36.200 --> 14:38.630
[Wei Residence]

14:43.140 --> 14:44.870
[Received Grace, Cherished Favor]

14:57.480 --> 14:59.200
Prime Minister, please save me.

14:59.200 --> 15:00.730
Someone wants to depose me.

15:07.600 --> 15:08.530
Prime Minister,

15:09.240 --> 15:10.870
I'll be obedient from now on.

15:11.630 --> 15:13.230
All that happened in the past

15:13.320 --> 15:15.720
was because
I was deceived by the Li family.

15:26.270 --> 15:26.870
Prime Minister!

15:26.870 --> 15:27.440
Your Majesty!

15:27.440 --> 15:28.030
Prime Minister!

15:28.030 --> 15:28.840
Your Majesty!

15:28.870 --> 15:30.810
Your Majesty, as the Emperor,

15:30.840 --> 15:33.550
you should conduct yourself
with proper dignity.

15:33.550 --> 15:35.880
How can you lose your composure like this?

15:45.470 --> 15:48.030
Are rebel forces at the gates,

15:48.200 --> 15:51.550
or is someone staging a coup?

15:53.240 --> 15:54.080
Neither.

15:56.030 --> 15:58.830
The Palace still stands,
and the walls are intact.

15:59.240 --> 16:01.960
Then why are you so panicked,
Your Majesty?

16:04.350 --> 16:07.190
I—I've lost my composure.

16:18.810 --> 16:20.940
Li Xiang returned from Jizhou

16:20.970 --> 16:22.910
and said that rumors
were spreading in the army

16:22.910 --> 16:26.310
that a descendant
of the former Eastern Palace had appeared.

16:27.760 --> 16:29.040
Seventeen years ago,

16:29.420 --> 16:31.550
you did everything
to put me on the throne.

16:31.550 --> 16:33.720
I know that in this world,

16:34.200 --> 16:36.580
only you will always stand on my side.

16:37.150 --> 16:39.350
I trust no one but you.

16:52.270 --> 16:53.320
Your Majesty.

16:56.750 --> 16:57.690
Prime Minister.

16:59.150 --> 17:01.690
I... I am truly flustered.

17:02.840 --> 17:05.300
Rumors regarding the former Eastern Palace

17:05.349 --> 17:08.030
have surfaced
several times over the last decade.

17:08.030 --> 17:09.589
I will handle it.

17:10.589 --> 17:11.920
However, Your Majesty,

17:12.240 --> 17:14.720
the late Emperor abdicated to you,

17:14.720 --> 17:17.240
and you inherited the throne legitimately.

17:18.109 --> 17:19.920
What is there to worry about?

17:21.550 --> 17:23.480
Your Majesty, you must not forget

17:23.920 --> 17:25.640
that this time in the Northwest,

17:25.640 --> 17:28.800
there is a new general
with outstanding merit

17:29.000 --> 17:31.200
who saved the people from suffering

17:31.200 --> 17:32.590
and won their hearts.

17:32.590 --> 17:33.400
Your Majesty,

17:34.030 --> 17:36.480
you must take this opportunity
to win her over.

17:36.480 --> 17:38.880
Only then can you reassure the people

17:39.480 --> 17:41.920
and demonstrate your authority.

17:42.480 --> 17:45.680
Prime Minister,
you mean that butcher girl, Fan Changyu?

17:50.160 --> 17:52.480
This woman is indeed brave

17:52.640 --> 17:55.240
and did kill Lord Changxin
on the battlefield.

17:55.910 --> 17:57.550
But she comes from humble origins

17:57.550 --> 17:59.280
and has no foundation in court.

17:59.510 --> 18:01.200
How could she be of use to me?

18:01.720 --> 18:03.350
Don't forget,

18:03.350 --> 18:07.070
she commands half the forces in Jizhou,

18:07.090 --> 18:09.680
and the Li family wants to win her over.

18:10.160 --> 18:13.750
If you can summon her
to the capital to reward her

18:13.750 --> 18:16.960
for her repeated military achievements,

18:17.720 --> 18:21.690
it will demonstrate your vast grace.

18:24.510 --> 18:25.270
Alright.

18:25.600 --> 18:26.390
Excellent.

18:27.070 --> 18:29.200
Then I will follow your suggestion

18:29.480 --> 18:30.750
and issue my decree immediately,

18:30.750 --> 18:33.200
summoning Fan Changyu and the generals
who earned merit in quelling the rebellion

18:33.200 --> 18:34.690
to the Capital to receive their rewards.

18:34.690 --> 18:37.310
Great Yin now
has its first mighty female general.

18:37.310 --> 18:39.680
I will personally hold
the investiture ceremony for them.

18:39.680 --> 18:41.540
Your Majesty, you're truly wise.

18:48.400 --> 18:50.000
The Qi family is full of lies.

18:50.110 --> 18:51.970
They're all equally despicable.

18:52.510 --> 18:54.570
You must be careful, Prime Minister.

18:54.640 --> 18:58.050
Even the Emperor
knows about the former Eastern Palace.

18:59.200 --> 19:01.810
Is he planning to stop hiding it?

19:06.000 --> 19:07.750
Is Xie Jiuheng

19:09.020 --> 19:11.890
trying to become the next Wei Yan?

19:24.030 --> 19:26.140
His Majesty decrees:

19:26.200 --> 19:29.270
The rebellious Lord Changxin
plotted against the western borders.

19:29.270 --> 19:32.720
The female general Fan Changyu
fought valiantly

19:32.720 --> 19:34.830
and executed
the rebel leader on the battlefield.

19:34.830 --> 19:36.560
I commend her achievements

19:36.590 --> 19:39.480
and hereby appoint her
as Flower-Crowned General,

19:39.750 --> 19:41.560
rank Fourth Grade,

19:41.750 --> 19:43.560
with a Purple-gold Fish Pouch.

19:43.640 --> 19:46.550
You are to enter the Capital
to pay your respects

19:46.550 --> 19:48.480
and receive your title.

19:48.720 --> 19:50.400
Flower-Crowned General!

19:50.800 --> 19:51.590
Look here!

19:52.680 --> 19:54.160
So this is the Capital.

19:54.310 --> 19:55.440
Look at these buildings,

19:55.440 --> 19:57.330
this road, and these people.

19:57.400 --> 19:58.680
Mancang, pinch me.

19:58.680 --> 19:59.790
Am I dreaming?

20:00.370 --> 20:02.030
It hurts. We're not dreaming.

20:02.440 --> 20:03.590
Behave yourselves.

20:03.590 --> 20:04.960
Don't let people see

20:04.960 --> 20:06.690
that we're from the countryside.

20:06.690 --> 20:07.820
So what?

20:09.030 --> 20:10.510
Fan carved her way
to her position as General

20:10.510 --> 20:13.410
from the countryside
with a butcher knife.

20:13.480 --> 20:14.940
Who dares look down on her?

20:18.880 --> 20:21.400
Look at our female general. She's so cool.

20:21.920 --> 20:23.640
If General Fan were a man,

20:23.640 --> 20:24.720
I'd want to marry him.

20:24.720 --> 20:26.550
Maybe General Fan has brothers?

20:26.550 --> 20:29.030
If I can't marry her,
being her sister-in-law would be fine too.

20:29.030 --> 20:30.750
I never imagined that on horseback,

20:30.750 --> 20:32.350
she'd look more handsome than young men.

20:32.350 --> 20:33.400
I heard His Majesty

20:33.400 --> 20:36.130
will personally hold
the investiture ceremony.

20:36.200 --> 20:36.920
Really?

20:36.920 --> 20:39.750
General Fan is mighty!

20:40.070 --> 20:41.240
General Fan!

21:02.450 --> 21:06.500
[Guo's Wine House]

21:45.240 --> 21:47.200
His Majesty has decreed

21:47.350 --> 21:50.640
that Li Huai'an,
Discipline Inspector of Jizhou,

21:50.880 --> 21:56.200
and Flower-Crowned General Fan Changyu
are to pay their respects.

22:02.750 --> 22:03.330
[Diligent and Virtuous]

22:14.790 --> 22:17.920
Long live Your Majesty.

22:19.000 --> 22:20.110
You may rise.

22:20.550 --> 22:21.950
Thank you, Your Majesty.

22:23.920 --> 22:26.350
My beloved ministers, take a look.

22:27.240 --> 22:30.650
These are the backbone of our Great Yin.

22:34.310 --> 22:36.700
[Diligent and Virtuous]

22:39.440 --> 22:41.040
I am unworthy of such praise.

22:41.590 --> 22:42.770
To serve Your Majesty with loyalty

22:42.770 --> 22:43.960
is a subject's duty.

22:44.750 --> 22:46.960
Moreover, in this battle
against the rebels,

22:46.960 --> 22:48.200
those with the greatest merit

22:48.200 --> 22:50.190
were General He and the Marquis of Wu'an.

22:50.190 --> 22:54.900
[Diligent and Virtuous]

22:50.720 --> 22:52.530
General He and the Marquis of Wu'an

22:52.530 --> 22:54.740
are indeed the pillars of Great Yin.

22:57.270 --> 22:59.330
General He died in battle at Lucheng.

22:59.960 --> 23:01.480
I am heartbroken.

23:01.790 --> 23:03.680
I couldn't eat for days.

23:04.400 --> 23:07.240
Fortunately, Great Yin
has the Marquis of Wu'an

23:07.240 --> 23:09.510
and loyal subjects like you.

23:09.510 --> 23:13.680
That's why these ministers and I
can rest easy.

23:14.790 --> 23:17.520
I will not fail your expectations,
Your Majesty.

23:18.110 --> 23:20.680
I heard that among the people
of Great Yin,

23:20.680 --> 23:22.340
a female general has emerged.

23:22.480 --> 23:24.350
Step forward and let me see.

23:26.680 --> 23:28.030
I, Fan Changyu,

23:28.550 --> 23:29.830
greet Your Majesty.

23:29.890 --> 23:31.690
[Diligent and Virtuous]

23:30.550 --> 23:31.790
Come closer.

23:39.910 --> 23:42.650
I, Fan Changyu, greet Your Majesty.

23:44.910 --> 23:45.840
Raise your head.

23:49.530 --> 23:51.630
What a fine warrior peony.

23:55.150 --> 23:56.720
Are you married?

23:58.270 --> 24:00.920
Your Majesty, I already have a husband.

24:03.200 --> 24:05.110
Where is your husband now?

24:06.960 --> 24:08.590
During the conscription early this year,

24:08.590 --> 24:10.520
my husband went to the front lines.

24:11.240 --> 24:12.720
I was desperate to find him

24:13.070 --> 24:15.200
and joined the army by accident
on the way.

24:15.200 --> 24:17.460
But the Battle of Lucheng was too brutal.

24:17.830 --> 24:18.960
My husband...

24:19.380 --> 24:20.900
remains missing.

24:21.070 --> 24:22.480
Missing, you say?

24:22.590 --> 24:23.920
Then why don't you...

24:36.270 --> 24:38.400
In my 17 years on the throne,

24:38.510 --> 24:40.830
I have never seen a female general.

24:41.270 --> 24:43.130
I was just overcome with emotion.

24:44.720 --> 24:46.750
Fan, in quelling the rebellion,

24:46.750 --> 24:47.920
killed Shi Hu first,

24:47.920 --> 24:49.440
and then beheaded Lord Changxin.

24:49.440 --> 24:51.590
Her contribution is truly remarkable.

24:51.590 --> 24:54.830
I hereby appoint her
as Flower-Crowned General,

24:54.830 --> 24:58.130
and bestow upon her the title
of Imperial Madame of the Fourth Rank.

24:58.130 --> 24:59.770
Why is she conferred such a high rank?

24:59.770 --> 25:00.960
What happened?

25:05.080 --> 25:06.370
I, Fan Changyu,

25:05.910 --> 25:07.960
[Diligent and Virtuous]

25:06.400 --> 25:08.660
thank Your Majesty for your great grace.

25:11.350 --> 25:13.820
[Diligent and Virtuous]

25:15.400 --> 25:16.230
Your Majesty,

25:16.640 --> 25:18.700
since the founding of our dynasty,

25:18.830 --> 25:20.750
there has never been a female general

25:20.750 --> 25:23.190
holding a rank above the fifth grade.

25:23.480 --> 25:26.270
Appointing her Flower-Crowned General
is already unprecedented.

25:26.270 --> 25:27.110
Let alone...

25:27.110 --> 25:28.270
It seems the Grand Tutor's faction

25:28.270 --> 25:30.640
still can't bear to part with
that half of the military power.

25:30.640 --> 25:32.570
Please reconsider, Your Majesty.

25:39.030 --> 25:39.830
Your Majesty.

25:40.400 --> 25:42.260
General Fan is no ordinary woman.

25:42.480 --> 25:44.900
She beheaded Lord Changxin
and ended the war in one stroke.

25:44.900 --> 25:46.030
The primary credit belongs to her.

25:46.030 --> 25:47.490
Discipline Inspector Li,

25:48.510 --> 25:50.370
be careful not to speak out of turn

25:50.440 --> 25:51.970
in His Majesty's presence.

25:53.240 --> 25:54.650
I heard

25:54.880 --> 25:57.400
that before joining the army, General Fan

25:57.510 --> 26:00.550
was a butcher girl in a border town.

26:01.310 --> 26:03.070
I wonder how

26:03.200 --> 26:06.930
she managed to kill Lord Changxin,
the bravest in the Three Armies.

26:07.350 --> 26:08.070
Could it be...

26:08.070 --> 26:10.600
Thank you for the compliment,
Grand Tutor Li.

26:11.480 --> 26:14.180
I am just a village woman.

26:14.510 --> 26:15.770
I don't know much else,

26:15.830 --> 26:19.200
but I know pork must be cut precisely,

26:19.310 --> 26:21.510
and enemies must be killed ruthlessly.

26:22.790 --> 26:23.720
General Fan,

26:24.030 --> 26:26.940
this is not your filthy pigsty.

26:27.240 --> 26:29.790
Now that you are a court official,

26:29.790 --> 26:32.430
you must watch your words and actions
at all times.

26:32.430 --> 26:34.680
Especially in court,

26:34.680 --> 26:38.030
and especially before His Majesty
and the Grand Tutor.

26:38.030 --> 26:39.790
You are right, My Lord.

26:41.160 --> 26:42.510
Speaking of pigsties,

26:42.720 --> 26:44.030
the one at my home

26:44.030 --> 26:45.350
is swept clean,

26:45.350 --> 26:46.960
and the pigs are fat and strong.

26:46.960 --> 26:48.440
But there are always some bad pigs

26:48.440 --> 26:51.310
that like to piss and shit everywhere,

26:51.590 --> 26:53.830
making even the cleanest place dirty.

26:54.510 --> 26:55.070
You...

26:58.310 --> 26:59.880
Who are you calling a pig?

27:00.070 --> 27:01.160
Don't be angry, My Lord.

27:01.160 --> 27:02.620
I didn't say you were a pig.

27:04.480 --> 27:05.790
Fan, you are amusing.

27:06.200 --> 27:08.070
Your words are blunt,

27:08.270 --> 27:09.830
but they make some sense.

27:12.680 --> 27:13.440
General Fan.

27:13.440 --> 27:16.160
Sharp words
do not count as military merit.

27:16.400 --> 27:17.880
As a military commander,

27:17.880 --> 27:20.510
your duty is to protect the country,

27:20.830 --> 27:24.160
not to show off your sharp tongue here.

27:24.270 --> 27:26.070
You are right, Grand Tutor Li.

27:26.590 --> 27:29.850
Of course I know the importance
of protecting the country.

27:30.270 --> 27:33.200
But when the people
on the border were suffering,

27:33.480 --> 27:36.410
where were you making snide remarks,
Grand Tutor Li?

27:36.720 --> 27:37.270
You...

27:39.350 --> 27:40.550
Alright, alright.

27:42.240 --> 27:44.920
General Fan
certainly has a straightforward character,

27:44.920 --> 27:47.380
completely different from ordinary women.

27:48.680 --> 27:52.000
No wonder you achieved
such illustrious military merits.

27:52.110 --> 27:55.790
As they say,
a hero's background doesn't matter.

27:56.030 --> 27:58.400
We, the court officials,

27:58.880 --> 28:01.750
should be tolerant of her.

28:03.310 --> 28:05.400
As for the military power,

28:05.720 --> 28:07.520
we shall discuss it another day.

28:10.000 --> 28:12.240
Thank you, Prime Minister Wei.

28:12.920 --> 28:14.960
That I can stand here today

28:15.400 --> 28:18.240
is thanks to your magnanimity.

28:24.000 --> 28:27.190
However, I don't think
this is just a battle of words.

28:27.640 --> 28:29.480
The Imperial Court
is like butchering pigs.

28:29.480 --> 28:30.750
There must be rules.

28:30.960 --> 28:33.000
Butchering requires a single fatal cut.

28:33.000 --> 28:35.400
Speaking in court
should also hit the mark.

28:35.400 --> 28:36.680
With so much beating around the bush,

28:36.680 --> 28:38.210
how can problems be solved?

28:38.310 --> 28:40.030
Just like the Battle of Lucheng—

28:40.030 --> 28:42.480
if the soldiers had all cowered back,

28:42.590 --> 28:44.450
who would have defended Lucheng?

28:44.750 --> 28:47.550
General Fan,
every word you say makes sense,

28:47.960 --> 28:50.440
but your language is uncouth.

28:50.960 --> 28:54.880
You really must learn some etiquette
in the future.

28:55.270 --> 28:56.920
You are right, Prime Minister Wei.

28:56.920 --> 28:58.880
I really need to work on my tendency

28:58.880 --> 29:00.410
to speak without thinking.

29:00.880 --> 29:01.510
Oh, right.

29:02.000 --> 29:03.240
The Marquis of Wu'an asked me

29:03.240 --> 29:06.500
to offer incense at his parents' tomb
to report his safety.

29:10.030 --> 29:10.750
Prime Minister Wei,

29:10.750 --> 29:13.160
would you like to pay respects
to your sister

29:13.160 --> 29:14.490
and General Xie as well?

29:31.110 --> 29:32.000
My beloved ministers,

29:32.000 --> 29:33.730
if there is nothing else today,

29:34.310 --> 29:35.440
court is dismissed.

29:35.880 --> 29:40.350
Speak now or the court is dismissed!

29:41.240 --> 29:43.480
Farewell, Your Majesty.

30:01.110 --> 30:02.480
It's a nice place,

30:03.030 --> 30:04.960
but there aren't many good people.

30:06.030 --> 30:07.830
It can't even compare to Lin'an.

30:12.240 --> 30:13.000
General Fan.

30:16.070 --> 30:18.800
You shouldn't have made so many enemies
in court.

30:22.640 --> 30:23.440
Grandfather.

30:26.880 --> 30:29.080
So you still know I am your grandfather?

30:30.160 --> 30:30.790
Go back.

30:38.200 --> 30:39.830
General Fan, please wait.

30:42.960 --> 30:44.440
I am not your grandson.

30:44.460 --> 30:46.520
What? Are you going to lecture me too?

30:48.000 --> 30:51.080
Your demeanor in the hall today

30:51.160 --> 30:53.880
truly impressed me.

30:53.880 --> 30:56.200
Now that you have been praised
by His Majesty,

30:56.200 --> 30:58.790
and everyone calls you a heroine,

30:58.990 --> 31:00.910
but as a woman,

31:01.030 --> 31:03.760
sooner or later you must marry
and have children.

31:03.880 --> 31:05.810
No matter how high your merits are,

31:05.920 --> 31:07.920
this is the ceiling.

31:08.750 --> 31:11.110
A sparrow can never fly to the top branch,

31:11.400 --> 31:13.680
nor can it become a phoenix.

31:14.640 --> 31:16.350
A woman who's married and has children

31:16.350 --> 31:17.810
can still achieve merits.

31:18.680 --> 31:19.510
Besides,

31:20.110 --> 31:21.710
what business is it of yours?

31:22.000 --> 31:23.920
General Fan, have you heard the saying,

31:23.920 --> 31:27.110
"A wise man submits to circumstances"?

31:28.720 --> 31:29.400
Fine.

31:30.480 --> 31:33.540
I will now "submit to circumstances"
and take my leave.

31:50.160 --> 31:50.830
My Lord.

31:51.440 --> 31:53.570
Grand Tutor, your sedan chair is nice.

31:55.110 --> 31:55.790
My Lord.

32:00.310 --> 32:02.270
Getting carried away with success...

32:02.270 --> 32:05.680
she'll fall hard sooner or later.

32:19.200 --> 32:19.790
My Lord!

32:19.960 --> 32:20.690
Grand Tutor!

32:20.880 --> 32:22.280
My Lord, are you alright?

32:23.830 --> 32:24.440
My Lord!

32:24.440 --> 32:26.000
How dare you...

32:27.240 --> 32:29.480
Fan Changyu.

32:33.670 --> 32:35.040
Prime Minister Wei was pissed off,

32:35.040 --> 32:36.790
and the Grand Tutor stumbled out
of his sedan chair.

32:36.790 --> 32:38.680
The Princess Royal is here!

32:39.720 --> 32:40.720
Sister!

32:41.110 --> 32:41.830
Sister!

32:43.030 --> 32:44.450
What makes you so happy?

32:44.730 --> 32:49.840
[Speak with Caution]

32:45.270 --> 32:47.790
Do you know General Fan
came to court today?

32:48.000 --> 32:49.920
She is truly an extraordinary figure.

32:49.920 --> 32:51.200
Let me tell you, Sister.

32:51.200 --> 32:52.070
Since I ascended the throne,

32:52.070 --> 32:54.310
I have never laughed
as heartily as I did today.

32:54.310 --> 32:54.920
Tell me,

32:54.370 --> 32:56.020
[Speak with Caution]

32:54.920 --> 32:56.380
what kind of person is she?

32:56.720 --> 32:58.070
Changyu...

32:58.680 --> 33:01.030
Changyu has a straightforward nature.

33:01.030 --> 33:02.400
She is honest and adorable.

33:02.400 --> 33:03.920
Her martial arts are outstanding.

33:03.920 --> 33:05.520
She is sincere to her friends

33:05.680 --> 33:07.310
and willing to die for her comrades.

33:07.310 --> 33:09.710
And towards
the Marquis of Wu'an, she is...

33:11.310 --> 33:13.510
How is she towards the Marquis of Wu'an?

33:14.000 --> 33:16.640
Do not reveal my relationship with Changyu
after returning to the Capital.

33:16.640 --> 33:19.100
I fear someone
might use it to cause trouble.

33:20.720 --> 33:22.400
She holds the Marquis of Wu'an
in high esteem.

33:22.400 --> 33:24.000
They are comrades-in-arms.

33:26.450 --> 33:28.550
So, this Fan Changyu can not only fight,

33:28.550 --> 33:30.210
but also influence Xie Zheng.

33:30.270 --> 33:32.000
I was worried that there was no one
I could use in court.

33:32.000 --> 33:34.000
This girl suits my needs perfectly.

33:37.270 --> 33:38.070
Grandfather,

33:38.750 --> 33:40.750
although Qi Min is a royal grandson,

33:41.070 --> 33:42.400
he is not a worthy lord.

33:42.870 --> 33:44.400
He is perverse and violent,

33:44.550 --> 33:46.150
and his methods are vicious.

33:46.480 --> 33:49.210
If our Li family helps him
regain imperial power,

33:49.790 --> 33:51.270
when he comes into power,

33:52.510 --> 33:55.400
it will be a time
of suffering for the common people.

33:55.830 --> 33:57.350
Now, Qi Sheng

33:57.350 --> 33:59.010
is merely Wei Yan's puppet.

33:59.030 --> 34:01.690
He is unworthy of his position
and incompetent.

34:01.750 --> 34:03.440
As for Wei Yan's nature—

34:03.830 --> 34:05.510
you don't need me

34:05.680 --> 34:07.480
to tell you.

34:08.110 --> 34:09.670
In past wars,

34:09.670 --> 34:11.880
he completely disregarded
the lives of the people,

34:11.880 --> 34:13.739
forcibly requisitioning grain.

34:13.920 --> 34:16.550
The people were starving and displaced.

34:16.550 --> 34:18.510
The tragic scene
of starved corpses littering the fields

34:18.510 --> 34:20.550
was all caused by him.

34:20.760 --> 34:22.070
Such behavior

34:22.230 --> 34:24.150
is truly cruel and inhumane.

34:24.150 --> 34:27.670
That is what truly makes
the people suffer.

34:27.670 --> 34:29.000
But Qi Min's cruelty

34:29.000 --> 34:30.280
far exceeds that of Wei Yan.

34:30.280 --> 34:31.760
I saw it with my own eyes.

34:34.360 --> 34:35.190
Grandfather,

34:36.550 --> 34:39.080
our Li family
has been loyal for generations.

34:39.590 --> 34:41.400
We must not help a tyrant do evil

34:42.030 --> 34:45.070
and let such a despicable person
ascend the throne.

34:45.440 --> 34:47.510
But he is the descendant
of Crown Prince Chengde,

34:47.510 --> 34:49.920
bearing the legitimate blood
of the imperial family.

34:49.920 --> 34:51.000
All these years,

34:51.130 --> 34:53.760
he has been wandering
and suffering hardships.

34:53.760 --> 34:56.480
It is inevitable that his temperament
has become unstable.

34:56.480 --> 34:58.230
You should try to understand him

34:58.230 --> 35:00.440
and not judge him rashly.

35:00.710 --> 35:02.170
Haven't you thought about

35:02.360 --> 35:04.630
that we might be cast aside
once we've served our purpose?

35:04.630 --> 35:06.510
Grandson,

35:07.510 --> 35:09.110
your Master, He Jingyuan,

35:09.190 --> 35:11.150
was principled and righteous.

35:12.150 --> 35:15.080
He was a top-tier meritorious official
of Great Yin.

35:15.150 --> 35:18.230
He died fighting on the battlefield!

35:18.710 --> 35:21.000
In the end, it was all for nothing.

35:21.000 --> 35:23.110
No matter how much you emphasize
national righteousness,

35:23.110 --> 35:24.630
what good will it do?

35:25.920 --> 35:29.650
Then you shouldn't have sent me
to the Northwest in the first place.

35:30.190 --> 35:32.110
Think it through.

35:32.570 --> 35:33.880
Is the current Emperor

35:34.110 --> 35:36.440
a wise ruler or a tyrant?

35:36.550 --> 35:37.840
Is he beneficial

35:38.400 --> 35:40.360
to the nation?

35:57.710 --> 35:58.440
My Lord.

36:00.550 --> 36:02.400
Have men surround the study immediately.

36:02.400 --> 36:03.880
If he dares to act rashly,

36:03.880 --> 36:04.940
confine him at once

36:05.190 --> 36:06.650
and then report back to me.

36:06.960 --> 36:07.590
Yes.

36:08.670 --> 36:10.270
Qi Min has been taken care of.

36:10.400 --> 36:11.360
He is right at...

36:16.750 --> 36:18.580
[Jingque Pavilion]

36:20.230 --> 36:21.070
Come here.

36:21.550 --> 36:23.230
My Lord, what are you doing?

36:23.360 --> 36:24.710
Stop it, My Lord.

36:24.920 --> 36:26.230
Where are you going?

36:26.880 --> 36:28.510
We haven't finished the wine yet.

36:28.510 --> 36:30.510
Don't run away, little lady. Little lady!

36:30.510 --> 36:31.440
My Lord.

36:33.110 --> 36:34.800
General Fan, come in and join the fun.

36:34.800 --> 36:36.460
Yeah, General Fan, come on in.

36:37.000 --> 36:38.630
No thanks. You guys enjoy.

36:39.280 --> 36:39.920
Well...

36:40.710 --> 36:41.300
My Lord,

36:41.330 --> 36:41.960
come catch me!

36:41.960 --> 36:43.020
Alright, alright.

36:44.290 --> 36:46.480
Socializing? What does socializing mean?

36:46.480 --> 36:48.110
It means hanging out
with a bunch of strangers,

36:48.110 --> 36:49.310
eating and drinking.

36:49.710 --> 36:51.320
After that, you become acquaintances.

36:51.320 --> 36:53.380
Why don't you socialize with me a bit?

36:53.510 --> 36:54.570
Socialize with me.

36:57.220 --> 36:58.350
[Jingque Pavilion]

37:04.760 --> 37:05.670
General Fan.

37:04.850 --> 37:10.450
[Jingque Pavilion]

37:06.190 --> 37:07.920
General Fan, until next time.

37:07.920 --> 37:08.560
Until next time.

37:08.560 --> 37:09.510
Until next time.

37:09.920 --> 37:12.440
-My Lord, let me see you off.
-My Lord, you're not drunk, are you?

37:12.440 --> 37:13.710
Come again next time.

37:13.710 --> 37:14.590
Sure, sure.

37:17.590 --> 37:18.400
Let's go, Fan.

37:18.670 --> 37:19.710
I'm going for a walk.

37:19.710 --> 37:20.710
You guys go ahead.

37:21.000 --> 37:22.110
Don't forget me.

37:22.670 --> 37:23.550
I won't.

37:28.320 --> 37:29.000
Clothes.

37:30.840 --> 37:31.710
Wait here.

37:31.840 --> 37:32.900
I'll go take a look.

38:03.490 --> 38:06.000
♪ The moon is as quiet as me ♪

38:06.780 --> 38:08.400
♪ The light shines ♪

38:09.080 --> 38:11.750
♪ It illuminates
the turbulence in my heart ♪

38:12.250 --> 38:14.870
♪ It seems to be the fire of love ♪

38:15.430 --> 38:17.230
♪ Just a few sparks ♪

38:17.690 --> 38:22.520
♪ Let me hide in your heart ♪

38:18.520 --> 38:19.780
Why are you here?

38:21.160 --> 38:22.120
I missed you.

38:24.990 --> 38:26.230
♪ I pray that our love ♪

38:26.250 --> 38:28.790
♪ Will never end ♪

38:29.420 --> 38:30.590
♪ It's worth my foolishly waiting ♪

38:30.610 --> 38:32.860
♪ For a lifetime ♪

38:33.640 --> 38:37.560
♪ Clear and quiet as me ♪

38:37.940 --> 38:47.400
♪ Why do we need
to seek cause and effect ♪

38:54.760 --> 38:56.480
Aren't you afraid of being seen?

38:56.480 --> 38:57.760
It doesn't matter.

38:57.840 --> 39:00.590
I was worried
since it's your first time in the Capital.

39:00.590 --> 39:01.710
But seeing how

39:02.280 --> 39:05.150
our Flower-Crowned General
handled things with ease,

39:05.150 --> 39:06.110
I was relieved.

39:12.000 --> 39:13.200
None of the officials

39:13.550 --> 39:14.480
care about the truth

39:14.480 --> 39:16.190
from 17 years ago.

39:17.440 --> 39:19.760
Those stories in the shadow puppet plays,

39:19.760 --> 39:23.070
about voicing grievances before the throne
and getting justice,

39:23.070 --> 39:24.800
where good and evil are judged,

39:24.800 --> 39:25.710
are all fake.

39:27.070 --> 39:28.800
And the Emperor is unreliable.

39:32.000 --> 39:32.920
Don't worry.

39:33.510 --> 39:35.440
I'll go with you to find the truth.

39:37.670 --> 39:39.530
We will clear your father's name.

39:47.280 --> 39:48.030
Thank you.

39:55.490 --> 39:56.110
Let's go home.

39:56.110 --> 39:57.790
Go home? We won't wait for Sister?

39:57.790 --> 39:58.920
Didn't you say
there are many bad people in the Capital?

39:58.920 --> 40:00.380
Shouldn't we protect her?

40:00.400 --> 40:01.110
Right.

40:01.130 --> 40:02.440
Today in the Golden Celestial Hall,

40:02.440 --> 40:03.980
the Emperor asked Sister
if she had a husband.

40:03.980 --> 40:05.030
What does he want?

40:05.590 --> 40:06.670
That bastard Emperor.

40:06.670 --> 40:08.020
He definitely wants Sister
to be his consort.

40:08.020 --> 40:09.920
He can't have any good intentions.

40:09.920 --> 40:11.050
You're catching on.

40:11.800 --> 40:13.360
Stop babbling here.

40:14.630 --> 40:16.360
With the Marquis of Wu'an here,

40:16.560 --> 40:18.360
no one in this world can hurt her.

40:20.580 --> 40:22.240
You're worrying for nothing.

40:23.590 --> 40:25.550
Pointless. Truly pointless.

40:27.870 --> 40:28.880
Go back.

40:29.880 --> 40:31.340
I'll take a walk by myself.

40:35.930 --> 40:38.750
[Prudent in Action, Mindful of Peril]

40:53.710 --> 40:55.320
Greetings, Your Majesty.

40:55.880 --> 40:57.070
Dear ministers.

40:57.320 --> 40:59.050
What do you have to report to me?

40:59.670 --> 41:02.630
Your Majesty, I have a matter to report.

41:02.760 --> 41:04.800
That Flower-Crowned General, Fan Changyu,

41:04.800 --> 41:06.550
is arrogant and oversteps her bounds,

41:06.550 --> 41:08.440
a disgrace to the integrity of Great Yin.

41:08.440 --> 41:10.400
She not only contradicted
Prime Minister Wei,

41:10.400 --> 41:12.230
but was also disrespectful to me.

41:12.230 --> 41:14.490
Your Majesty, I hope you will punish her.

41:16.840 --> 41:19.150
Prime Minister Wei,
are you also here to impeach General Fan?

41:19.150 --> 41:20.630
No, Your Majesty.

41:21.800 --> 41:25.630
I am here
to request a reward for General Fan.

41:27.840 --> 41:31.190
Didn't you mention the rumors

41:31.190 --> 41:33.110
about the former Eastern Palace
a few days ago?

41:33.110 --> 41:35.110
I have investigated it thoroughly.

41:35.670 --> 41:37.590
General Fan not only

41:37.800 --> 41:39.000
killed Lord Changxin on the battlefield,

41:39.000 --> 41:40.400
earning great merit,

41:40.840 --> 41:46.030
but she also saved the bloodline
of Crown Prince Chengde,

41:46.670 --> 41:48.400
the Imperial Great-Grandson.

41:50.760 --> 41:54.150
He is the legitimate grandson
of the former Eastern Palace.

41:54.590 --> 41:57.550
General Fan has achieved
a great merit this time.

41:57.840 --> 42:00.030
Her bravery should be commended.

42:03.150 --> 42:07.150
What... joyous news for the nation.

42:07.400 --> 42:08.530
Prime Minister Wei,

42:09.080 --> 42:12.430
the imperial bloodline
concerns the legitimacy of the state.

42:12.430 --> 42:13.710
It cannot be confused.

42:14.070 --> 42:16.320
Seventeen years ago,
the Eastern Palace caught fire.

42:16.320 --> 42:19.440
Crown Princess Chengde and the legitimate
Imperial Grandson both died.

42:19.440 --> 42:20.320
So,

42:20.880 --> 42:24.190
how could this Imperial Great-Grandson
appear out of nowhere?

42:24.190 --> 42:25.400
And where is he

42:25.920 --> 42:27.480
now?

42:27.920 --> 42:29.710
After the battle of Lucheng,

42:29.710 --> 42:32.590
the Imperial Great-Grandson
indeed went missing.

42:33.000 --> 42:35.590
I request a decree to issue a bounty

42:36.030 --> 42:38.550
to search for the Imperial Great-Grandson
throughout the country.

42:38.550 --> 42:41.670
If we can truly find
the imperial bloodline this time,

42:42.190 --> 42:45.550
it would relieve Your Majesty's worries
about succession.

42:47.320 --> 42:49.760
As for whether he is real or fake,

42:49.990 --> 42:52.710
there must be ways to verify it.

42:53.000 --> 42:54.670
Even if there is a slight chance,

42:54.670 --> 42:55.960
we cannot give up.

42:56.190 --> 42:57.110
Only in this way

42:57.510 --> 43:01.880
can we be worthy
of the late Emperor's vast grace.

43:05.630 --> 43:07.880
Prime Minister Wei, you're right.

43:08.070 --> 43:09.670
As for the bounty,

43:09.760 --> 43:11.220
I entrust you to handle it.

43:12.840 --> 43:15.230
You must... You must find...

43:15.420 --> 43:17.030
my poor nephew.

43:23.550 --> 43:26.410
Grandfather, please calm down.
Watch your health.

43:27.510 --> 43:30.630
Does the Marquis of Wu'an
really have luck on his side?

43:31.030 --> 43:33.150
He clearly committed heinous crimes,

43:33.150 --> 43:35.210
but they keep getting cancelled out.

43:37.760 --> 43:38.510
No.

43:39.110 --> 43:40.230
No matter what,

43:40.430 --> 43:41.920
I must make this uncle and nephew

43:41.920 --> 43:44.280
completely turn on each other!

43:52.280 --> 43:53.740
Send someone immediately

43:54.110 --> 43:57.190
to get word to Xie Zheng
by any means necessary.

43:57.510 --> 43:59.030
Tell him that 17 years ago,

43:59.400 --> 44:01.510
on the way returning to the capital,

44:01.510 --> 44:03.370
Wei Yan received a letter from Qi.

44:03.510 --> 44:06.310
That caused the deaths of his father,
Xie Linshan,

44:06.400 --> 44:09.060
and Crown Prince Chengde
of the Eastern Palace.

44:09.840 --> 44:12.300
But that letter
has long since disappeared.

44:12.480 --> 44:14.670
That bastard Wei might have destroyed it.

44:14.670 --> 44:16.880
A rumor is all we need.

44:16.900 --> 44:19.760
Xie Zheng will look for the evidence.

44:20.110 --> 44:23.190
We just need to let the two of them

44:23.760 --> 44:25.630
fight it out.

44:32.000 --> 44:33.710
Seventeen years ago,

44:34.280 --> 44:37.440
Wei Yan was a man of many attachments.

44:37.930 --> 44:42.260
That's why
it led to today's great catastrophe.

44:44.320 --> 44:45.480
Today,

44:46.150 --> 44:47.350
let's just

44:48.400 --> 44:50.320
set up another trap.

44:56.550 --> 44:59.200
[Post-Credits Scene]

44:59.610 --> 45:03.470
[Where Compassion and Grace Meet]

45:02.920 --> 45:05.280
Your Majesty, I am here!

45:09.030 --> 45:10.230
I knew it!

45:10.630 --> 45:12.110
Of all the officials at court,

45:12.110 --> 45:13.320
not a single one treats me

45:13.320 --> 45:15.400
as the true Emperor!

45:16.000 --> 45:18.550
Wei Yan treats me like a puppet.

45:19.000 --> 45:21.130
Does Xie Zheng also want to do the same—

45:21.590 --> 45:23.550
find a descendant
of the former Eastern Palace

45:23.550 --> 45:25.440
and use him as a puppet?

45:25.550 --> 45:28.320
Li Xiang, you... you are useless!

45:28.760 --> 45:30.190
You even missed the information

45:30.190 --> 45:32.070
that the former Eastern Palace
has a descendant

45:32.070 --> 45:33.760
still alive in this world!

45:33.810 --> 45:34.880
Even you...

45:34.880 --> 45:35.920
Do you also want to

45:35.920 --> 45:38.320
serve a different emperor?

45:38.400 --> 45:40.440
Do you?

45:40.510 --> 45:41.480
No!

45:41.550 --> 45:44.480
Please calm your anger, Your Majesty!

45:44.480 --> 45:46.710
Do not let my mistakes

45:46.710 --> 45:49.230
harm your health.

45:49.880 --> 45:50.710
Your Majesty,

45:51.400 --> 45:55.510
I have really tried my best this time.

45:56.360 --> 46:00.190
The Princess Royal
wouldn't help me either.

46:00.450 --> 46:02.680
With no other choice,

46:02.710 --> 46:07.320
I risked my life
to break into that military tent.

46:07.320 --> 46:08.000
But...

46:08.400 --> 46:12.630
I had an ear cut off by His Lordship!

46:14.070 --> 46:15.150
Your Majesty!

46:15.570 --> 46:18.960
I know I am useless.

46:19.880 --> 46:20.590
But...

46:21.760 --> 46:24.150
in my heart,

46:24.670 --> 46:26.360
truly,

46:26.360 --> 46:30.880
there is only you, Your Majesty.

46:32.070 --> 46:33.800
Come forward.

46:38.960 --> 46:41.320
I am here.

46:42.550 --> 46:43.960
Does it hurt?

46:47.710 --> 46:50.000
I... I am fine.

46:50.360 --> 46:53.670
It's better now.

46:54.480 --> 46:56.710
N-No matter if it's Wei Yan...

46:57.300 --> 46:58.640
or Xie Zheng,

46:58.670 --> 47:00.840
no one can sit on this dragon throne!

47:01.230 --> 47:02.320
It is mine!

47:02.320 --> 47:03.670
No one else can!

47:03.960 --> 47:05.510
Yes, Your Majesty.

47:05.760 --> 47:07.710
You are the true Son of Heaven.

47:08.000 --> 47:10.800
Those people are not worthy!

47:10.800 --> 47:13.920
No, you... you promise me

47:14.230 --> 47:15.480
that you will serve me
for the rest of your life.

47:15.480 --> 47:16.680
That I am the Emperor.

47:20.800 --> 47:21.840
Yes,

47:23.880 --> 47:25.480
Your Majesty!
